{
  "page": "On a Misty Morn",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Tim_Durning_On_A_Misty_Morn.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/03/Tim_Durning_On_A_Misty_Morn.jpg/350px-Tim_Durning_On_A_Misty_Morn.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/03/Tim_Durning_On_A_Misty_Morn.jpg/525px-Tim_Durning_On_A_Misty_Morn.jpg 1.5x, /images/0/03/Tim_Durning_On_A_Misty_Morn.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Tim_Durning_On_A_Misty_Morn.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>\"On a Misty Morn\", by Tim Durning © FFG</div></div></div>\n<p>\"<b>On a Misty Morn</b>\" is a song about a mother searching for her son among the dead, and the grief that she feels. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Lyrics\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Lyrics</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Lyrics\">Lyrics</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=On_a_Misty_Morn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Lyrics\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"font-style:italic;padding-left:1em;display:flow-root;\" class=\"poem\">\n<p>Oh, have you seen my boy, good ser?<br />\n<span class=\"mw-poem-indented\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 1em;\">His hair is chestnut brown</span><br />\nHe'd promised he'd come back to me<br />\n<span class=\"mw-poem-indented\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 1em;\">Our home's in <a href=\"/index.php/Wendish_Town\" title=\"Wendish Town\">Wendish Town</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=On_a_Misty_Morn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=On_a_Misty_Morn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>It is sung by <a href=\"/index.php/Marillion\" title=\"Marillion\">Marillion</a> while in his <a href=\"/index.php/Sky_cell\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sky cell\">sky cell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=On_a_Misty_Morn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_10\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 10\">Chapter 10</a>, Sansa I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403152333\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.016 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.017 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 204/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8638/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 778/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 208/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 1/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1323/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    8.243      1 -total\n 64.47%    5.314      1 Template:Lyrics\n 63.29%    5.217      2 Template:Ref\n 40.59%    3.346      2 Template:Ref/core\n 18.37%    1.514      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:5270-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403152333 and revision id 276397\n -->\n",
